summary: This is a retexture of the small towns, villages, inns/taverns, watermills, farms and other related stuff in Skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
[center][/center][img]http://s4.postimg.org/my31oss3h/Title.png[/img]

This is a retexture of the farmhouse package.
This package handles all textures of the small towns, villages, inns/taverns, watermills, farms and other related stuff in Skyrim.

Check the images for more...
[b]Note: [/b]the images are [u]NOT[/u] taken with an ENB preset. They are vanilla, taken with [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/27043/?]ELFX Weathers[/url] plus my [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/62925/?]ELFX Revised Weather[/url] mod.
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/65163/?][img]http://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/65163-1-1430071785.png[/img][/url]
[u][b]Installation
[/b][/u]This package comes in two flavors. Pick the one of your choice, and unzip it into your Skyrim\Data\ folder. Let it overwrite previous textures. Alternatively, you can use your favorite mod manager.

[u][b]Credits
[/b][/u]Some of this work is derivative of work from:
[b]LucidAPs - [/b]check out his mod: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/50595/?
[b]AnOldFriend - [/b]check out his mod:Â http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/7255/?
